{"tid":1383184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記唔記得就嚟取消銀行最低餘額","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:10:25.000Z","uid":143987,"like":101,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"699d86707d6e456cb178ed53caaa6677279f3cf5","tid":1383184,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"8月1日就係中銀、匯豐、渣打同花旗取消個人戶口總值下限、並取消低額結存服務費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要記得將中銀嘅錢轉晒去另外三間銀行<br />\n<br />\n而用中銀做出糧戶口都唔緊要<br />\n可以係出糧個陣過數<br />\n<br />\n而家網上銀行服務咁方便  <br />\n做多一兩步都唔會好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然換左出糧嘅銀行就仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到中銀越嚟越少錢就爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得同身邊仲用緊中銀嘅人講呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d96214058119354f33884cd79d2fbca886d458","tid":1383184,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"934729ada3e44e6f877812913b1abe16c3546b09","tid":1383184,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e3065af903f834209cd18870a95f0598ab81e23","tid":1383184,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f2c0a4844bc0fc3f1fda7ae6559c37b1f17bf78","tid":1383184,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a119b0c9f13ce08c2e83e5d728796df2713e2da3","tid":1383184,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"八月一日 提走中資！"},{"pid":"e506d76dee82fec78338b8895a3281c3c46a214e","tid":1383184,"uid":115212,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":